node.text:
Strong alone. Unstoppable together. Join athlete @SashaDigiulian in the #NewBentayga.
_
Bentayga V8 WLTP drive cycle: combined fuel consumption: 21.2 mpg (13.3 l/100 km), combined CO₂: 302 g/km

node.title: Find your extraordinary with the New Bentayga.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bentley Motors Official on July 23, 2021. May be an image of bottle.

node.text:
Our partnership with @The_Macallan is one based on a shared vision – to become one of the most sustainable luxury brands out there.

--

Please drink responsibly. Do not drink and drive.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bentley Motors Official on July 22, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The epitome of craftsmanship and contemporary design that have defined Bentley for years, the Flying Spur and the Bentayga. Both, now simply electrifying.

Shot at @the_macallan Estate.

#BentleyHybrids #SustainableLuxury

----

Bentley #FlyingSpurHybrid is available to order in most markets, but is currently not available in EU27, UK, Switzerland, Israel, Ukraine, Norway, Turkey and Vietnam.

#Bentley #Bentayga Hybrid WLTP drive cycle: fuel consumption, mpg (l/100 km) – Combined, weighted 83.1 (3.4). Combined, weighted CO₂ – 82 g/km.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bentley Motors Official on July 21, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
How do you improve the Bentley Continental GT?

Easy, you take the roof off and enjoy the sunshine.

#BentleyContinentalGT

Photos by @thekirill_k at @ramp.space

----

#Bentley #Continental GT V8 Convertible WTLP drive cycle: combined fuel consumption: 22.6 mpg (12.5 l/ 100 km), combined CO2: 284 g/km
